collection.name: Crypto Bull Society
collection.description:
The Crypto Bull Society is a group of like-minded individuals who are bullish on the future of crypto. 

Our mission is to increase the GDP of Web 3.0, while trolling the hell out of each other.

Membership is represented by holding a Crypto Bull or Crypto Bear NFT, from our unique private art collection.

Every holder of a Crypto Bull @ 8 February was entitled to claim a Crypto Bear for free.

Check out the Crypto Bear NFT collection: https://opensea.io/collection/crypto-bears-by-cbs
